WEBVTT

01:42.400 --> 01:47.120
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:50.000 --> 01:51.440
YIXIANG RESTAURANT

01:51.520 --> 01:53.280
You are the owner, Ms. Yu,
of Yixiang Restaurant?

01:54.080 --> 01:55.240
Yes.

01:55.320 --> 01:56.640
-Take her away.
-Yes.

01:58.640 --> 01:59.800
Okay.

01:59.880 --> 02:01.200
I'll go with you to the Yamen.

02:17.800 --> 02:18.720
It's me.

02:20.120 --> 02:21.760
The Magistrate has ordered.

02:21.840 --> 02:23.880
Yixiang Restaurant will remain sealed

02:23.960 --> 02:25.440
until the murder case is solved.

02:26.040 --> 02:28.320
This is to prevent evidence
from being destroyed.

02:28.400 --> 02:30.280
-Guard this building strictly.
-Yes.

02:34.160 --> 02:35.000
Why are you here?

02:35.080 --> 02:37.160
You were gone so long, I came to check.

02:38.120 --> 02:39.360
I'm fine.

02:39.440 --> 02:40.760
It's Qian who's in trouble.

02:40.840 --> 02:42.720
I plan to kidnap that damned Magistrate
to rescue Qian.

02:42.800 --> 02:44.400
You take Ning and hide.

02:44.480 --> 02:47.120
If I'm captured, take good care of her.

02:47.200 --> 02:49.160
-Who gave you that stupid idea?
-Me.

02:51.320 --> 02:52.680
I was just making a hypothesis.

02:52.760 --> 02:55.560
Don't worry, I'll strike
when the Magistrate is alone.

02:55.640 --> 02:56.480
I won't get caught.

02:58.200 --> 02:59.520
Kidnapping him is useless.

03:00.440 --> 03:03.000
People with an agenda are using
the grain levy to incite the villagers.

03:03.080 --> 03:04.760
Yixiang Restaurant’s case
is just the beginning.

03:04.840 --> 03:08.000
They are deliberately driving the people
to go against the Yamen,

03:08.080 --> 03:10.440
so Jizhou troops will come
and suppress the rioters,

03:10.520 --> 03:11.960
thereby sealing

03:12.040 --> 03:14.040
the rumor as a fact that the government's
grain levy drove the people to rebel.

03:15.480 --> 03:16.960
How do you know all this?

03:19.320 --> 03:20.240
I'll tell you later.

03:21.320 --> 03:23.280
Go find Chief Constable Wang now.

03:23.360 --> 03:25.400
Have him and his constables
guard the city gate at all costs.

03:25.480 --> 03:26.560
We absolutely cannot
let the rioters enter the city.

03:28.440 --> 03:29.320
Wait!

03:29.840 --> 03:30.880
If the rioters enter the gate,

03:30.960 --> 03:33.240
they'll come for the Magistrate
and his men.

03:33.320 --> 03:35.680
Why should I stop the rioters for them?

03:35.760 --> 03:37.840
These people have been
driven to this state.

03:37.920 --> 03:39.400
Is it just justice they want?

03:39.480 --> 03:40.680
Once they're inside,

03:40.760 --> 03:43.000
none of the officials
and wealthy families will be spared.

03:43.760 --> 03:45.040
One step further,

03:45.120 --> 03:47.280
they too can be rebel soldiers
who burn, kill, and loot.

03:50.000 --> 03:51.800
What if the authorities
don't release the grain?

03:55.440 --> 03:58.200
Just calm the rioters first.
I'll figure out the rest.

03:59.240 --> 04:00.160
Alright.

04:00.680 --> 04:03.320
l'll take Bao'er with me
on my way to Chief Constable Wang.

04:03.400 --> 04:04.640
No.

04:04.720 --> 04:07.480
I have another way
to guarantee his safety.

04:17.600 --> 04:19.279
If you really can't control the rioters,

04:21.360 --> 04:22.840
you must protect yourself.

04:31.280 --> 04:32.160
Bye.

04:46.640 --> 04:48.120
You there! What are you doing?
What are you holding?

04:49.920 --> 04:51.040
I'm talking to you! Stop!

04:52.080 --> 04:53.040
That child…

04:53.120 --> 04:54.640
-You stay here and guard.
-Okay.

04:55.840 --> 04:56.760
Come, Bao'er.

05:00.720 --> 05:02.200
Yixiang Restaurant is safe now.

05:02.280 --> 05:05.240
Hide in the secret room.
Don't make a sound, no matter who calls.

05:05.320 --> 05:06.480
Understood, Auntie Changyu.

05:06.560 --> 05:08.960
You must save my mother.

05:09.040 --> 05:11.440
Don't worry, I'll definitely save her.

05:11.520 --> 05:12.360
Go.

05:17.000 --> 05:19.520
QINGPING COUNTY YAMEN

05:19.600 --> 05:22.400
YAMEN

05:25.480 --> 05:27.240
Any news from the scouts?

05:28.120 --> 05:29.600
Has Wei Xuan brought his men?

05:30.800 --> 05:32.560
No messages back yet.

05:36.200 --> 05:39.440
Those grain seized from merchants
and commoners of Qingping County.

05:39.520 --> 05:40.600
Get it out of here first.

05:41.480 --> 05:44.000
The 1,000 soldiers of ours
are still waiting outside.

05:44.080 --> 05:45.480
SUI YUANQING
ELDEST SON OF PRINCE CHANGXIN

05:45.560 --> 05:47.800
If that useless Wei doesn't come,

05:48.320 --> 05:50.680
we'll kill some rioters on his behalf.

05:57.120 --> 05:59.600
But these rioters are coming
to join our Chongzhou.

05:59.680 --> 06:01.440
Why would the Prince kill them?

06:04.120 --> 06:06.600
No need to kill them all. Just for show.

06:06.680 --> 06:10.080
Just make sure the common people
lose all faith in the government.

06:12.560 --> 06:15.040
If we don't cut off
all retreat for these rioters,

06:15.120 --> 06:17.000
they won't sincerely join our Chongzhou.

06:19.960 --> 06:22.040
Have we caught that little brat
from Yixiang Restaurant?

06:23.440 --> 06:24.800
He was rescued.

06:24.880 --> 06:26.600
But I sent men to pursue.

06:26.680 --> 06:28.800
We should know the updates soon.

06:30.720 --> 06:32.080
Don't harm the child.

06:32.600 --> 06:34.600
-After all, he is my elder brother's son.
-Yes.

06:37.960 --> 06:40.320
And the woman in the prison?

06:40.400 --> 06:43.560
She's my elder brother's concubine.

06:43.640 --> 06:45.520
Take her back and let
elder brother decide himself.

06:45.600 --> 06:48.040
Just make sure no one humiliates her.

06:50.720 --> 06:51.680
Yes.

06:59.840 --> 07:00.840
Miss.

07:00.920 --> 07:04.120
Long time no see. You still look so good.

07:04.640 --> 07:07.880
Yan will soon go to the capital
for the exams.

07:07.960 --> 07:09.880
He has been thinking of you often.

07:10.560 --> 07:12.640
So he had me buy some little trinkets

07:12.720 --> 07:14.560
and bring them especially for you.

07:18.640 --> 07:20.800
-Xiaolu.
-Yes.

07:21.440 --> 07:24.240
-That's very kind of him.
-Not at all.

07:24.320 --> 07:25.160
Anything else?

07:25.240 --> 07:28.880
Your mom recently praised
my shoe patterns.

07:28.960 --> 07:30.880
So today I brought them specially.

07:30.960 --> 07:32.800
Thought I'd give them to her
over teatime later.

07:32.880 --> 07:34.080
Give them to her.

07:34.960 --> 07:36.680
Mother has caught a slight cold.

07:36.760 --> 07:38.600
She is not yet recovered,
not suitable for visitors.

07:38.680 --> 07:40.920
I thank you on her behalf, Auntie.

07:41.480 --> 07:43.920
Xiaolu, see our guest off.

07:44.000 --> 07:46.160
-Yes.
-Then I won't disturb you.

07:46.240 --> 07:48.480
-I'll come another day.
-Bye, Madam Song.

07:48.560 --> 07:49.800
Okay.

07:58.960 --> 08:00.240
What the hell?

08:01.000 --> 08:03.280
Really thought she's some noble lady.

08:03.800 --> 08:05.640
Just a Magistrate's daughter.

08:05.720 --> 08:08.360
Does she really think my son
will kneel to her and beg for marriage?

08:10.160 --> 08:11.960
Shameless enough to accept gifts,

08:12.480 --> 08:15.480
but not even offer to go in for tea!

08:15.560 --> 08:17.640
-What kind of person is that?
-Move!

08:17.720 --> 08:19.160
IMMACULATE AND LUMINOUS

08:19.240 --> 08:20.240
Hurry, hurry!

08:22.720 --> 08:23.640
Get in quickly!

08:23.720 --> 08:25.200
-What are you dawdling for? Get in!
-How dare you!

08:26.720 --> 08:28.600
-No tricks!
-Open up!

08:41.600 --> 08:44.320
‎THE PONDERING PAVILION

09:08.720 --> 09:09.840
‎-Let's go.
‎-Sure.

09:13.640 --> 09:14.880
They're all fake constables.

09:15.760 --> 09:16.800
Miss!

09:18.080 --> 09:20.800
Perhaps you should have some soup.

09:20.880 --> 09:23.400
What time is it,
and you're talking about soup?

09:26.520 --> 09:27.600
What was that noise?

09:34.760 --> 09:35.720
Who's there?

09:37.720 --> 09:40.040
You are… Fan Changyu!

09:44.280 --> 09:45.120
Why are you here?

09:45.840 --> 09:48.520
Never mind. I'll just lie about it.
Less explaining to do.

09:49.440 --> 09:50.880
Constable Wang sent me.

09:52.080 --> 09:54.560
He sensed something was wrong
at the Yamen these past few days.

09:55.720 --> 09:56.720
Indeed, the old are more experienced.

09:56.800 --> 09:58.760
A few days ago,
a gang of people came up to us.

09:58.840 --> 10:00.040
Their leader…

10:00.120 --> 10:03.560
claimed to be the Northwest
Military Commissioner Wei Xuan.

10:04.200 --> 10:05.480
He took my father hostage,

10:05.560 --> 10:08.440
and forced him to requisition
silver and grain in the county.

10:08.520 --> 10:09.760
And Clerk Guo…

10:09.840 --> 10:12.280
He turned traitor to save himself!

10:12.360 --> 10:13.480
It was him again!

10:14.160 --> 10:15.360
No wonder he's so shameless.

10:17.120 --> 10:18.520
Miss Fan.

10:18.600 --> 10:20.800
Before, when I fought with you
over Song Yan,

10:20.880 --> 10:21.840
I was immature.

10:21.920 --> 10:23.600
Don't take it to heart.

10:24.960 --> 10:27.320
My father is in Wei Xuan's hands now.

10:28.800 --> 10:30.280
I beg you.

10:30.360 --> 10:31.920
Help me save my father.

10:35.040 --> 10:36.120
Song Yan…

10:38.640 --> 10:39.480
Song Yan…

10:39.560 --> 10:42.080
-I'll give Song Yan to you.
-No, no.

10:43.000 --> 10:44.840
You keep Song Yan for yourself.

10:44.920 --> 10:46.400
If you really want to thank me,

10:46.480 --> 10:48.000
after this is done,

10:48.080 --> 10:49.480
go to the prison and release Ms. Yu.

10:49.560 --> 10:51.320
No problem. I promise.

10:51.400 --> 10:53.400
As long as I can save my father,
I'll do anything

10:58.440 --> 11:00.320
Can I borrow your maid's clothes?

11:00.840 --> 11:03.960
QINGPING

11:10.240 --> 11:12.000
-Go…
-Go…

11:12.080 --> 11:14.440
-Return our grain!
-Those behind, follow!

11:15.400 --> 11:16.800
Follow!

11:16.880 --> 11:18.280
Make the damned Magistrate
return the grain!

11:18.360 --> 11:20.040
Make the damned Magistrate
return the grain!

11:20.120 --> 11:21.040
Follow us!

11:22.040 --> 11:23.600
Return the grain!

11:30.520 --> 11:32.160
They're trying to storm the city!

11:32.800 --> 11:34.080
Close the gate!

11:34.160 --> 11:35.160
Quick, close the gate!

11:39.400 --> 11:41.200
Not seeing Magistrate Cui
at the Yamen for days…

11:42.280 --> 11:44.000
Fortunately, Fan Changyu's husband

11:44.080 --> 11:46.680
sensed something was wrong
and arranged defenses in advance.

11:46.760 --> 11:48.880
Otherwise, there'd be big trouble.

11:52.080 --> 11:55.160
All of you, stay sharp.
Put on Jizhou army uniforms.

11:55.240 --> 11:56.320
Wait for the inside help

11:56.400 --> 11:58.360
to open the gate for the Prince.

11:58.440 --> 12:00.880
-We can catch them off guard and attack!
-Yes.

12:09.600 --> 12:10.720
Let us in!

12:11.320 --> 12:12.680
Let us in!

12:12.760 --> 12:14.360
Let me in!

12:16.120 --> 12:17.520
Let us in!

12:18.880 --> 12:19.720
Let us enter!

12:20.640 --> 12:23.200
We want to leave! Why is the gate closed?

12:23.280 --> 12:24.680
Quick, move aside!

12:25.200 --> 12:27.000
-Move aside! Move aside!
-Let us out!

12:27.080 --> 12:28.520
-Disperse!
-Let us out quickly!

12:28.600 --> 12:30.160
-Let me out!
-Let me out!

12:30.240 --> 12:31.760
-We want to live!
-Let us out.

12:31.840 --> 12:33.800
If you keep talking,
you'll be the first to die.

12:33.880 --> 12:35.560
‎-Come out and die!
‎-Damned Magistrate!

12:35.640 --> 12:36.640
Come out and die!

12:36.720 --> 12:38.880
Damned Magistrate, come out and die!

12:39.600 --> 12:40.560
Disperse!

12:43.320 --> 12:44.280
General!

12:44.360 --> 12:46.760
The Magistrate sent a maid
to bring you some soup.

12:49.080 --> 12:50.080
Make her scram.

12:50.760 --> 12:52.880
This maid is quite pretty.

12:52.960 --> 12:54.320
The General said scram.

12:54.400 --> 12:55.800
-Didn't you hear?
-Yes.

12:57.520 --> 12:58.520
Wait!

13:02.320 --> 13:04.920
Wei Xuan is notorious
for being brutal and lustful.

13:05.440 --> 13:07.760
No reason for him
to suddenly become chaste.

13:10.000 --> 13:11.320
Fine, let her in.

13:12.240 --> 13:13.080
Yes.

13:24.200 --> 13:25.120
Sir.

13:37.720 --> 13:38.560
Please enjoy, sir.

13:45.720 --> 13:46.880
All shy and coy…

13:47.480 --> 13:48.680
Just to my taste.

13:49.760 --> 13:51.200
Put the food over there first.

13:52.240 --> 13:53.160
Yes.

13:57.560 --> 13:58.400
Is he Wei Xuan?

14:00.440 --> 14:04.000
Never mind. Whether he is or not,
tie him up first.

14:19.080 --> 14:20.080
General!

14:21.120 --> 14:22.840
You'd better not fall into my hands later.

14:23.520 --> 14:25.160
Otherwise, I'll definitely skin you

14:25.240 --> 14:26.560
and hang you at the city gate.

14:32.960 --> 14:34.600
You'd better have any day after today.

14:34.680 --> 14:36.040
Don't hurt the General!

14:36.560 --> 14:37.680
I won't hurt him,

14:38.200 --> 14:40.320
as long as you do as I say.

14:41.040 --> 14:42.720
Do as she says.

14:44.400 --> 14:46.040
I'll remember you.

14:47.080 --> 14:48.560
You better not remember me.

14:48.640 --> 14:50.400
I'm just following
our Magistrate's orders.

14:51.480 --> 14:52.640
Release my lord!

14:56.760 --> 14:58.960
Damn Magistrate, come out!

14:59.560 --> 15:00.440
Come out!

15:01.280 --> 15:03.920
Fellow villagers, what are you doing?

15:04.000 --> 15:05.920
Don't be rash

15:06.000 --> 15:08.320
and commit this crime
of extermination of the nine clans.

15:08.400 --> 15:09.680
The grain seeds

15:10.320 --> 15:11.800
will be returned to you.

15:12.720 --> 15:14.560
Everyone, go home now.

15:14.640 --> 15:15.560
Regarding this rebellion,

15:15.640 --> 15:17.520
we will not pursue it further.

15:18.600 --> 15:21.320
Fellow villagers!
Don't be fooled by this lackey!

15:21.960 --> 15:23.200
He's coaxing us to go home.

15:23.280 --> 15:24.400
What awaits us

15:24.480 --> 15:26.640
is the same fate as that in Ma Village!

15:26.720 --> 15:28.000
-Right!
-Yes!

15:28.080 --> 15:29.480
-Right!
-That's right!

15:29.560 --> 15:31.520
Villagers, charge into the city!

15:31.600 --> 15:32.920
Kill the damn official!

15:33.000 --> 15:34.040
Kill the damn official!

15:34.120 --> 15:36.760
Fellow villagers,
as for the Ma Village tragedy,

15:37.280 --> 15:39.920
we will definitely investigate
and give you an answer.

15:40.000 --> 15:41.360
Don't come any closer!

15:42.400 --> 15:43.920
If you advance further, we'll shoot!

15:49.360 --> 15:52.040
-Should we go?
-What do we do?

16:03.840 --> 16:06.000
Master, what a disaster!

16:06.080 --> 16:07.040
That 200,000 dan of grain

16:07.120 --> 16:08.800
was intercepted
on the way back to Chongzhou.

16:10.120 --> 16:11.000
Who did it?

16:11.080 --> 16:13.520
Seems two groups attacked
from front and back.

16:13.600 --> 16:15.600
One was Xie Zheng's Bloodclad Cavalry.

16:15.680 --> 16:16.960
The other was the Jizhou army.

16:17.040 --> 16:19.920
Wasn't He Jingyuan imprisoned
by that fool Wei Xuan?

16:22.160 --> 16:25.640
So Xie Zheng was colluding
with He Jingyuan all along.

16:27.360 --> 16:29.120
What a live-in son-in-law!

16:29.200 --> 16:31.080
What a Marquis Wu'an!

16:31.160 --> 16:33.560
He Jingyuan is Wei Yan's trusted follower.

16:33.640 --> 16:35.560
Xie Zheng is investigating Wei Yan's past.

16:35.640 --> 16:38.240
-How could they join forces?
-Who the hell knows?

16:38.920 --> 16:40.080
Report!

16:41.200 --> 16:42.960
Our men have successfully
infiltrated the rioters.

16:43.040 --> 16:45.080
A thousand Chongzhou elite troops
are also hidden outside the city.

16:45.160 --> 16:46.520
Ready to support Prince at any time.

16:47.080 --> 16:49.600
Master, although the grain
was intercepted,

16:49.680 --> 16:51.280
our counter-intelligence plan succeeded.

16:51.360 --> 16:53.560
Your careful planning is worthwhile.

16:55.400 --> 16:59.160
The more commoners die,
the greater the Wei faction's crime.

16:59.240 --> 17:02.480
The government forcibly levied grain,
driving a whole county to rebel.

17:02.560 --> 17:05.400
Such a huge crime, who can bear it?

17:07.520 --> 17:09.240
But now, I feel

17:10.160 --> 17:12.119
my good brother Sui Yuanqing

17:12.640 --> 17:15.400
has likely met his true match.

17:23.119 --> 17:24.880
THE PONDERING PAVILION

17:24.960 --> 17:27.240
Release the Yamen people,
or I'll kill him.

17:28.200 --> 17:29.040
Alright.

17:29.640 --> 17:30.920
Go ahead. Kill me.

17:31.000 --> 17:31.840
Listen!

17:31.920 --> 17:33.320
If I die,

17:33.400 --> 17:35.400
everyone here will be buried with me!

17:35.480 --> 17:36.320
Yes.

17:36.400 --> 17:39.040
Stop! I am here!

17:39.560 --> 17:41.640
Don't be impulsive!

17:41.720 --> 17:42.560
Don't be impulsive!

17:42.640 --> 17:44.400
Those outside the city are all rioters.

17:44.920 --> 17:46.440
They came today to slaughter.

17:47.480 --> 17:50.240
Release me, and I'll spare your lives.

17:50.320 --> 17:51.240
Slaughter?

17:56.880 --> 17:59.680
Slaughter? You dare to slaughter?

17:59.760 --> 18:00.800
Fine.

18:00.880 --> 18:02.520
I'll drag you up
to the city tower right now

18:02.600 --> 18:03.720
and see who shall live on.

18:06.600 --> 18:08.080
You're really interesting.

18:08.600 --> 18:10.200
I remember you.

18:13.840 --> 18:15.040
Again?

18:21.280 --> 18:22.280
Do it then.

18:22.360 --> 18:24.720
You'd better remember how you died.

18:25.840 --> 18:27.400
My men have released the Magistrate.

18:28.040 --> 18:29.760
You can release me now.

18:32.240 --> 18:33.280
These damned officials.

18:33.360 --> 18:35.760
When have they ever treated
our lives as human lives?

18:35.840 --> 18:37.200
Shoot then!

18:37.280 --> 18:38.240
If you shoot me dead,

18:38.320 --> 18:41.160
don't forget to collect my corpse!

18:41.240 --> 18:43.120
-Come on!
-Shoot! Shoot!

18:49.160 --> 18:50.280
Who gave the order to shoot?!

18:51.320 --> 18:53.440
Gouzi, are you okay? Gouzi!

18:53.520 --> 18:55.440
Wake up! Gouzi! Gouzi!

18:56.680 --> 18:59.160
Damn it! I'll fight you to the death!

18:59.240 --> 19:00.920
-Fight them to the death!
-Charge in!

19:01.000 --> 19:02.880
-Fight!
-Charge in!

19:04.720 --> 19:05.920
Charge in!

19:15.560 --> 19:17.960
Go for the ones who shot the arrows.

19:19.480 --> 19:21.320
Don't be incited by those with an agenda.

19:22.560 --> 19:23.760
You are…

19:23.840 --> 19:25.120
I am on your side.

19:30.000 --> 19:31.360
The Magistrate has been taken under guard.

19:31.440 --> 19:34.400
Those with red ribbons are all fake.
Have your men act without hesitation.

19:41.080 --> 19:43.520
-Seize these fake ones!
-Yes.

19:56.680 --> 19:57.880
Report!

19:58.480 --> 19:59.880
Rioters are gathered outside the gate.

19:59.960 --> 20:02.680
A few highly skilled men
seized the levied military grain.

20:02.760 --> 20:04.120
They are now transporting it
towards the county gate,

20:04.200 --> 20:07.120
say… saying they'll return it
to all the rioters.

20:07.200 --> 20:09.080
Yan Zheng succeeded.

20:09.760 --> 20:12.280
Your people had a thorough plan.

20:13.400 --> 20:16.200
But right now, this person
has become a hot potato.

20:16.280 --> 20:19.440
If I really kill him,
then I'll kill a high-ranked official.

20:19.520 --> 20:22.000
Probably I could only take Ning
to a bandit hideout for life.

20:23.280 --> 20:25.120
But if I release this man,

20:25.200 --> 20:26.960
I'll definitely have no peace later.

20:28.960 --> 20:29.880
Your Honor.

20:30.840 --> 20:32.200
People from Lin'an Town

20:32.280 --> 20:33.880
rebelled because of the grain levy.

20:33.960 --> 20:36.560
You must give them an explanation
to quell their anger.

20:37.480 --> 20:38.320
Well…

20:39.160 --> 20:41.160
I absolutely dare not decide this.

20:41.240 --> 20:43.880
The granary is right there. Just take it.

20:43.960 --> 20:45.880
I'll pretend I know nothing.

20:46.400 --> 20:47.480
Father!

20:47.560 --> 20:50.360
You are the Magistrate!

20:50.440 --> 20:51.320
If you say that,

20:51.400 --> 20:54.080
you're worse than
a pig-slaughtering woman! Coward!

20:54.160 --> 20:55.280
Shut up!

20:55.360 --> 20:56.880
What do you know?

20:56.960 --> 20:58.000
This is how it goes.

20:58.080 --> 21:00.520
Once those rioters enter the city, they
are sure to kill a few corrupt officials.

21:00.600 --> 21:01.720
Your father, as the Magistrate,

21:01.800 --> 21:03.040
will definitely
be the first one sacrificed.

21:03.120 --> 21:04.320
-You stop talking!
-You--

21:04.840 --> 21:06.800
The Magistrate,
with such a high-up position,

21:06.880 --> 21:08.360
yet is as timid as a mouse.

21:09.320 --> 21:10.440
I can only try with his daughter here.

21:12.680 --> 21:14.600
Miss, what should we do
with this damned official?

21:16.320 --> 21:17.440
Father!

21:17.520 --> 21:20.120
These rioters want an explanation, right?

21:20.200 --> 21:22.800
We should let him take the responsibility.

21:22.880 --> 21:25.440
Let them give the rioters an answer.

21:25.520 --> 21:27.200
That's right.

21:27.280 --> 21:29.120
Put the filth pot on his head.

21:29.200 --> 21:31.160
He is the best scapegoat.

21:32.280 --> 21:33.240
I understand.

21:34.960 --> 21:38.160
Grain levying was a military order
brought by you generals, correct?

21:38.760 --> 21:39.840
At this point,

21:39.920 --> 21:42.720
I must trouble you to go to the city gate

21:42.800 --> 21:43.760
and give the people an explanation.

21:43.840 --> 21:46.720
Fine. Then let's go to the city gate.

21:47.960 --> 21:49.720
I will give you an explanation.

21:52.600 --> 21:54.240
-Move aside!
-You there, take the Miss back.

21:54.320 --> 21:56.000
-Father, I'm coming too!
-Stay here.

21:57.480 --> 22:00.520
-Open the gate!
-Open the gate!

22:02.920 --> 22:04.200
Keep an eye on those inciters.

22:04.920 --> 22:06.480
Their actions are not like
ordinary villagers.

22:06.560 --> 22:07.560
‎Come out now!

22:08.800 --> 22:10.200
‎Get out!

22:10.280 --> 22:11.640
‎Come out and die!

22:11.720 --> 22:14.160
Come out and die! Come out and die!

22:15.520 --> 22:16.360
Fellow villagers.

22:17.160 --> 22:19.760
The grain levied before
will definitely be returned to you.

22:20.520 --> 22:21.800
You are all honest, law-abiding people.

22:21.880 --> 22:23.680
Don't be used by those with an agenda.

22:23.760 --> 22:25.000
Don't make a grave mistake.

22:25.080 --> 22:27.400
For those willing to take their grain
and return home,

22:27.480 --> 22:29.880
today's matter ends here.

22:29.960 --> 22:31.120
We will not pursue it.

22:31.880 --> 22:34.360
The Jizhou army is already on the way
to Qingping County.

22:34.960 --> 22:36.920
If you break through this gate today,

22:37.000 --> 22:38.240
there will be no turning back.

22:38.320 --> 22:39.640
For the rest of your lives,

22:39.720 --> 22:41.880
do you want to keep farming
with your wives, parents, and children

22:42.400 --> 22:44.000
or drag your whole family
to the underworld?

22:44.080 --> 22:46.320
It all depends on your choice.

22:46.400 --> 22:48.400
Words are empty. Where's the grain?

22:48.480 --> 22:49.640
Right, where's the grain?

22:49.720 --> 22:52.600
-Where's the grain?
-Then where is it?

22:52.680 --> 22:55.480
-Where's the grain?
-The grain is here!

23:00.320 --> 23:01.920
-Grain!
-It's grain!

23:02.000 --> 23:04.600
-It really is grain!
-The grain is here!

23:04.680 --> 23:06.440
‎The grain is here!

23:07.920 --> 23:09.280
Fellow villagers.

23:09.360 --> 23:12.000
-Your grain is being transported out.
-Keep it steady.

23:12.080 --> 23:13.040
Steady.

23:15.640 --> 23:16.520
Hurry, hurry!

23:22.280 --> 23:23.120
‎Be quick!

23:23.200 --> 23:25.560
-It's grain!
-It really is grain!

23:25.640 --> 23:27.480
It really is grain!

23:27.560 --> 23:29.520
Grain! We are saved!

23:29.600 --> 23:31.800
We have grain!

23:34.360 --> 23:35.920
May I ask your name?

23:36.440 --> 23:38.160
Where might we meet in the future?

23:39.000 --> 23:41.680
I wouldn't want to miss such a fate.

23:41.760 --> 23:44.280
Someone is about to die. Less chatter.

23:45.880 --> 23:46.800
Constable Wang.

23:48.120 --> 23:49.480
How is the situation?

23:50.600 --> 23:51.720
My lord.

23:58.200 --> 23:59.040
Yan Zheng.

23:59.120 --> 24:00.760
My lord, this is…

24:02.320 --> 24:05.560
a general from Jizhou,
overseeing the grain levy.

24:05.640 --> 24:08.160
The matter caused full complaints
from people now.

24:08.240 --> 24:09.960
As their parental official,

24:10.040 --> 24:12.240
I had no choice but to defy my superiors.

24:12.320 --> 24:13.280
I tied up these military lords.

24:13.360 --> 24:15.320
I will definitely give
our people an answer.

24:16.000 --> 24:16.960
My lord is righteous!

24:18.760 --> 24:20.880
Now the rioters haven't entered the city.

24:20.960 --> 24:23.280
All thanks to Constable Wang
and your men guarding here.

24:24.080 --> 24:25.320
You did not fail me.

24:25.400 --> 24:26.880
I must confess.

24:27.400 --> 24:29.360
-Actually--
-The damned official up there!

24:29.440 --> 24:30.840
The grain issue is resolved.

24:30.920 --> 24:33.840
Then how do you compensate
for the dozen-plus lives from Ma Village?

24:33.920 --> 24:36.120
With the lives
of the damned Magistrate's family?

24:36.200 --> 24:38.960
-Exactly!
-Yes! Pay with your lives!

24:41.200 --> 24:42.520
Insolent commoners!

24:42.600 --> 24:44.400
You dare curse an imperial official!

24:44.480 --> 24:46.240
Did you all see?

24:46.320 --> 24:49.040
This damned Magistrate
doesn't see us as human at all!

24:49.680 --> 24:52.360
-He doesn't want to give us an answer!
-If we get coaxed back this time,

24:52.440 --> 24:54.640
just wait to be beaten to death
by these constables!

24:54.720 --> 24:56.080
-That's right!
-Kill the Magistrate!

24:56.160 --> 24:58.240
Kill the Magistrate!
Kill the damn officials!

24:58.840 --> 25:01.080
‎-Kill the Magistrate!
‎-Kill the damn officials!

25:01.160 --> 25:02.520
Kill the damn officials!

25:07.400 --> 25:08.560
Attack!

25:11.200 --> 25:13.280
‎Kill the damned Magistrate!

25:18.720 --> 25:19.800
Protect the Lord!

25:53.000 --> 25:54.560
-Whoa!
-Stop!

25:54.640 --> 25:57.040
My master sent me for a message.

25:57.120 --> 25:59.040
Chongzhou rebels has a small force

25:59.120 --> 26:00.880
hiding in the Nanshan woods of Lin'an.

26:00.960 --> 26:02.400
Please, Master, go intercept them

26:02.480 --> 26:04.520
to ensure the safety of Lin'an's people.

26:05.040 --> 26:06.160
Who is your master?

26:07.280 --> 26:09.600
My master's surname is Xie.

26:11.720 --> 26:12.920
All of you, obey my command!

26:13.560 --> 26:15.120
To protect Lin'an's people,

26:15.720 --> 26:16.920
fight by my side today.

26:17.000 --> 26:18.480
Kill and repel the enemy!

26:18.560 --> 26:20.840
-Attack!
-Attack!

26:36.360 --> 26:37.960
Game over.

26:38.760 --> 26:40.760
You think by bringing me here,

26:41.440 --> 26:42.840
you can stop all this?

26:43.520 --> 26:45.520
I'll still kill you,
even if I can't stop the game.

26:46.280 --> 26:47.600
You are looking for death!

27:06.440 --> 27:07.960
I didn't bring my butchering knives.

27:08.040 --> 27:09.960
Otherwise, I'd show you

27:10.040 --> 27:11.440
how New Year's pigs are bled.

28:12.160 --> 28:14.680
Wasn't it a small force?
Why are there reinforcements?

28:17.480 --> 28:18.560
We can't let them
pass through the snowy woods.

28:19.160 --> 28:21.200
Otherwise, the people
of Lin'an will suffer.

28:21.280 --> 28:22.160
We must hold.

28:49.720 --> 28:51.000
Master!

28:51.760 --> 28:53.680
The soldiers not of our Jizhou army,

28:54.320 --> 28:55.600
seize them all!

29:06.560 --> 29:07.640
General, retreat quickly!

29:07.720 --> 29:10.240
He Jingyuan's Jizhou army
is coming from the northeast!

29:10.320 --> 29:13.280
Our men of 1,000 soldiers are wiped out.

29:14.000 --> 29:15.840
Why did He Jingyuan come so fast?

29:15.920 --> 29:18.280
You can't run away. Catch him!

29:20.160 --> 29:21.800
General, don't go!

29:39.320 --> 29:40.600
Catch him!

29:44.280 --> 29:45.480
I've changed my mind.

29:46.400 --> 29:48.440
You'll come with me, be my concubine.

30:16.000 --> 30:17.800
I will go after him.
Meet at the usual place.

30:32.760 --> 30:33.720
The usual place?

30:35.160 --> 30:36.320
Where is it?

30:36.920 --> 30:41.200
‎QINGPING

30:45.800 --> 30:47.960
‎Lord He is here.

30:50.280 --> 30:52.000
-My lord!
-My lord!

30:52.080 --> 30:53.560
My lord!

30:53.640 --> 30:54.960
You must uphold justice for us!

30:55.040 --> 30:56.680
Show mercy, my lord!

30:56.760 --> 30:59.880
We were truly driven to it,
with no other way!

30:59.960 --> 31:01.520
Fellow villagers! Fellow villagers!

31:01.600 --> 31:04.480
Take your grain and go home now.

31:04.560 --> 31:07.200
There's more to the grain requisition.

31:07.720 --> 31:10.920
The incident in Ma Village will be
thoroughly investigated by the government.

31:11.000 --> 31:14.200
We will give you all a clear answer.

31:14.280 --> 31:17.360
-Thank you, my lord!
-Thank you!

31:20.600 --> 31:22.880
Don't rush. Line up and state your names.

31:22.960 --> 31:24.880
-There's enough for all.
-My grain is back!

31:24.960 --> 31:26.520
Don't grab. Everyone gets some!

31:28.960 --> 31:29.560
‎Zhao Hu.

31:29.640 --> 31:31.120
-My name…
-Okay.

31:31.200 --> 31:32.480
-Wang Zhixiang.
-Next.

31:39.640 --> 31:40.880
Lord He.

31:42.480 --> 31:44.040
Lord He.

31:44.680 --> 31:46.280
Luckily, you came.

31:46.360 --> 31:47.280
Otherwise,

31:47.360 --> 31:50.840
even if I filled the city wall
with my blood,

31:50.920 --> 31:53.480
I couldn't stop these rebels.

31:55.760 --> 31:56.760
Today,

31:56.840 --> 31:59.920
the people of Lin'an City are spared

32:00.720 --> 32:03.120
thanks to you, Magistrate Cui.

32:03.640 --> 32:05.360
I feel ashamed.

32:06.120 --> 32:07.560
The military grain requisition

32:07.640 --> 32:09.240
forced people to rebel.

32:09.320 --> 32:11.760
Fortunately, I saw through
their treacherous plot.

32:11.840 --> 32:13.880
Before the rioters entered,

32:13.960 --> 32:16.160
I dispatched constables
to block the city gates.

32:16.760 --> 32:18.720
That prevented the rioters from entering.

32:18.800 --> 32:21.320
I also defied my superiors.

32:21.400 --> 32:23.600
I tied up those officials
supervising the grain levy

32:23.680 --> 32:25.480
to quell public anger.

32:25.560 --> 32:27.840
It was extremely fortunate
Lord He arrived in time.

32:27.920 --> 32:30.880
We averted a disaster.

32:32.280 --> 32:34.280
You see, Constable Wang

32:34.360 --> 32:36.800
performed excellently under my command.

32:36.880 --> 32:38.880
He deserves a huge reward.

32:38.960 --> 32:40.360
I was just doing my duty.

32:41.200 --> 32:42.880
If my lord truly wishes to reward,

32:43.560 --> 32:47.080
give extra consolation money
to these dead and injured constables.

32:48.480 --> 32:49.880
In that case,

32:50.880 --> 32:54.760
all those who kept rioters
outside the gate,

32:54.840 --> 32:56.720
each should be rewarded.

32:57.400 --> 32:59.880
Thank you, my lord! Thank you!

32:59.960 --> 33:02.920
My lord, there is one more person
who should also be heavily rewarded.

33:03.000 --> 33:04.080
Who?

33:07.680 --> 33:08.520
Where is that girl?

33:10.320 --> 33:13.440
My lord, that girl he mentioned
is just my servant.

33:14.200 --> 33:16.560
Of course, she should also
be rewarded based on merit.

33:18.000 --> 33:19.560
Just now, from the city tower,

33:19.640 --> 33:21.800
I saw someone wearing a green demon mask.

33:21.880 --> 33:23.280
Who is that?

33:30.480 --> 33:33.520
Are you insane?
Why are you chasing me so hard?

33:34.040 --> 33:35.400
How did I offend you?

33:36.760 --> 33:39.840
Put down the crossbow,
and I'll spare your life.

33:40.600 --> 33:41.640
Who are you?

33:42.160 --> 33:43.560
What's your relation to that maid?

33:43.640 --> 33:46.760
Surely you're not too afraid
to give your name?

33:49.080 --> 33:49.960
Eldest Son of Prince Changxin,

33:51.720 --> 33:52.960
Sui Yuanqing.

34:21.480 --> 34:22.840
Marquis Wu'an,

34:24.040 --> 34:25.480
you're actually not dead?

34:34.679 --> 34:36.920
Who is that little maid
on the tower to you?

34:37.000 --> 34:38.760
Her skin is so fair.

34:40.000 --> 34:41.480
The taste when kissing it

34:42.639 --> 34:44.199
was truly sweet.

35:25.560 --> 35:26.520
Stop!

35:32.720 --> 35:33.800
Marquis Wu'an?

35:49.360 --> 35:50.760
After all these years,

35:50.840 --> 35:52.560
your martial arts haven't improved a bit.

35:53.360 --> 35:54.800
Marquis Wu'an didn't specify

35:55.400 --> 35:56.960
that was a troop
of a thousand Chongzhou elites.

35:57.760 --> 35:59.760
I commanded barely a hundred cavalry.

36:00.280 --> 36:02.040
That's one against ten.
I am still winning.

36:02.120 --> 36:05.280
Marquis Wu'an's Blood-clad Cavalry
is no better then this, right?

36:05.360 --> 36:07.400
If you were truly capable,

36:07.480 --> 36:09.920
even without intelligence,
you wouldn't be so disgraced.

36:10.720 --> 36:13.440
As a Commandant, using no strategy at all,

36:13.520 --> 36:14.840
just knows to charge forward and fight.

36:15.600 --> 36:17.400
I'll remember this.

36:17.480 --> 36:19.080
Once I'm healed,

36:19.160 --> 36:21.240
I'll have another contest with you.

36:21.320 --> 36:23.720
I'll definitely show you
what "disgraced" truly means.

36:26.480 --> 36:27.680
I look forward to it.

36:33.520 --> 36:35.880
How did their relationship
suddenly get so good?

36:35.960 --> 36:38.560
The one who impersonated Wei's envoy,
forging the grain levy order,

36:38.640 --> 36:41.440
and almost caused a revolt,
who exactly is he?

36:41.960 --> 36:42.800
Was he caught?

36:42.880 --> 36:45.480
Eldest Son of Prince Changxin,
Sui Yuanqing.

36:48.440 --> 36:50.320
Sui Yuanqing…

36:50.840 --> 36:53.200
He was truly as audacious
as the rumors say.

36:57.400 --> 36:59.640
If you wish to stabilize
the northwest situation,

36:59.720 --> 37:01.440
you will definitely
find use for me in the future.

37:02.200 --> 37:03.920
-How about we--
-I'm used to going my own way.

37:04.000 --> 37:06.280
I acknowledge your goodwill, Lord Li.

37:10.240 --> 37:11.960
Tang Peiyi said his attack this time

37:12.480 --> 37:14.200
was a pre-arranged plan
between you and my teacher.

37:14.280 --> 37:15.760
A surprise attack on enemy grain,

37:16.280 --> 37:19.160
intercepting 200,000 dan
of enemy provisions for the front.

37:21.360 --> 37:22.920
You can trust my teacher.

37:23.800 --> 37:25.120
Why not trust me?

37:33.280 --> 37:35.000
You know why, don't you?

37:35.960 --> 37:39.600
Are you worried that I am sent
by my grandfather to subvert the Wei's?

37:40.640 --> 37:43.480
My grandfather serves at court,
where politics are treacherous.

37:43.560 --> 37:46.240
Inevitably, he will have conflicts
with the Wei's.

37:47.560 --> 37:49.000
But I have my own aspirations.

37:50.880 --> 37:52.360
Namely, peace all over the world.

37:52.880 --> 37:55.240
The common people no longer suffer
the hardships of war.

37:55.320 --> 37:56.840
In the past,

37:56.920 --> 37:58.680
the Li family, in my eyes,

37:58.760 --> 38:00.480
was just a bunch
of self-serving opportunists.

38:01.080 --> 38:02.440
But after this battle,

38:02.960 --> 38:04.240
I can see it.

38:05.280 --> 38:06.200
You

38:07.360 --> 38:08.320
are not one of them.

38:11.640 --> 38:14.920
For now, I'll take your words
as a kind of praise.

38:17.880 --> 38:20.480
Are you planning to return
to the Yanzhou army camp now?

38:21.080 --> 38:23.280
I will stay with my teacher
to secure Lucheng

38:23.800 --> 38:25.920
and fight Prince Changxin to the death.

38:32.360 --> 38:33.280
What about you?

38:35.080 --> 38:36.320
I have my own plans.

38:39.040 --> 38:41.280
When you figure out which side you are on,

38:41.800 --> 38:43.320
come talk to me about a cooperation.

38:47.600 --> 38:50.360
Regarding Mrs. Fan, what are your plans?

38:53.080 --> 38:55.960
You might see this marriage as expediency,

38:57.000 --> 38:59.800
but for Mrs. Fan,
it's a true heart wasted.

39:00.320 --> 39:01.880
It seems rather cruel.

39:02.960 --> 39:04.160
This is my family issue.

39:05.000 --> 39:06.840
Lord Li shouldn't be worried about that.

39:56.520 --> 39:57.800
Why are you back so late?

39:59.200 --> 40:00.960
Are you hurt?

40:09.160 --> 40:10.200
I'm fine.

40:11.920 --> 40:13.320
That villain fell into the river.

40:14.560 --> 40:16.200
I pursued along the bank
for over ten miles.

40:16.280 --> 40:17.640
That's why I'm late.

40:18.960 --> 40:19.800
Don't worry.

40:35.080 --> 40:37.120
They say turtles live for millennia.

40:37.640 --> 40:40.360
That bastard won't turn into a turtle
and live immortal, right?

40:41.920 --> 40:42.840
He is definitely dead.

40:45.320 --> 40:48.000
Who is that maid on the tower to you?

40:48.520 --> 40:50.520
Her skin is so fair.

40:50.600 --> 40:52.720
The taste when kissing it

40:53.600 --> 40:55.400
was truly sweet.

41:06.120 --> 41:07.040
What's wrong?

41:08.560 --> 41:09.400
Nothing.

41:10.160 --> 41:12.600
Let me tell you.
When I went to catch the Magistrate,

41:12.680 --> 41:14.480
I happened to run into that bastard.

41:14.560 --> 41:16.480
Didn't expect he had some skills.

41:17.320 --> 41:18.440
My purlicue was injured from the shock.

41:29.160 --> 41:30.640
Shouldn't have let you go alone.

41:31.720 --> 41:34.560
It's fine. I tied him up
with rope all the way.

41:35.080 --> 41:37.920
And stabbed him several times.
Consider it revenge.

44:23.480 --> 44:26.960
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

44:27.040 --> 44:27.920
‎Subtitle translation by: Peng Peng
